(DevFlow Fullstack Architecture Guide) Tj
T*
(Generated: February 25, 2026) Tj
T*
T*
(1\) System Overview) Tj
T*
(DevFlow is a MERN-style application with a React + Vite frontend and an Express + MongoDB backend.) Tj
T*
(The frontend is responsible for user interaction, route-level navigation, local session persistence,) Tj
T*
(and data visualization.) Tj
T*
(The backend is responsible for authentication, role-based authorization, workspace state management,) Tj
T*
(business logic, and persistence.) Tj
T*
T*
(Core technologies used:) Tj
T*
(- Frontend: React 19, React Router, Axios, Recharts, Vite.) Tj
T*
(- Backend: Node.js, Express 5, Mongoose, JWT, bcrypt.) Tj
T*
(- Database: MongoDB \(single workspace document model plus users collection\).) Tj
T*
T*
(2\) Frontend Architecture) Tj
T*
(2.1 Entry and bootstrapping) Tj
T*
(- client/index.html contains the root mount node.) Tj
T*
(- client/src/main.jsx mounts App into #root under React.StrictMode.) Tj
T*
(- global styles are loaded from src/assets/styles/global.css.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.2 Routing model) Tj
T*
(- App.jsx defines BrowserRouter + top-level routes.) Tj
T*
(- Routes:) Tj
T*
( / and /signup -> Signup page) Tj
T*
( /login -> Login page) Tj
T*
( /home/* -> Home shell with nested routes \(tasks/chat/visualization\)) Tj
T*
( /home/contacts -> Contacts page) Tj
T*
( /home/management -> Management page) Tj
T*
( /home/profile -> Profile settings) Tj
T*
(- The /home/* catch-all makes TaskManager the fallback sub-view.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.3 API layer and auth token propagation) Tj
T*
(- src/services/api.js creates one Axios instance with baseURL http://localhost:3000/api.) Tj
T*
(- Request interceptor reads localStorage.authToken and injects Authorization: Bearer <token>.) Tj
T*
(- This centralizes authenticated API calls and avoids setting headers in each component.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.4 Authentication and user session UX) Tj
T*
(Signup flow \(Signup.jsx\):) Tj
T*
(- Performs light client-side validation \(name length, email format, password length\).) Tj
T*
(- Sends POST /users/signup with name/email/password/role.) Tj
T*
(- On success, shows success state and redirects to /login.) Tj
T*
T*
(Login flow \(Login.jsx\):) Tj
T*
(- Validates email/password format.) Tj
T*
(- Sends POST /users/login with email, password, and selected role.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
