(- On success stores token in localStorage.authToken and profile in localStorage.loggedInUser.) Tj
T*
(- Role-based navigation after popup:) Tj
T*
( management -> /home/management) Tj
T*
( team_member -> /home/tasks) Tj
T*
T*
(2.5 Home composition and role-aware navigation) Tj
T*
(Home.jsx:) Tj
T*
(- Fetches workspace summary once on mount \(GET /workspace\).) Tj
T*
(- Renders profile card from localStorage user + workspace team info from API.) Tj
T*
(- Renders nav links for tasks/chat/visualization/profile.) Tj
T*
(- Conditionally renders management link only if loggedInUser.role is management.) Tj
T*
(- Uses nested <Routes> to switch between TaskManager, TeamChat, Visualization.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.6 Task Manager behavior \(team member focus\)) Tj
T*
(TaskManager.jsx:) Tj
T*
(- Determines current user name from localStorage.) Tj
T*
(- Calls GET /workspace/tasks with query params:) Tj
T*
( assignedTo, page, limit, optional q, optional status, optional priority.) Tj
T*
(- Supports:) Tj
T*
( add task \(POST /workspace/tasks\)) Tj
T*
( toggle status \(PATCH /workspace/tasks/:id/toggle\)) Tj
T*
( search and filter \(status + priority\)) Tj
T*
( server-driven pagination via meta {total,page,limit,totalPages}) Tj
T*
(- Uses backend filtering instead of only local filtering, so pagination and counts stay consistent.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.7 Team chat behavior) Tj
T*
(TeamChat.jsx:) Tj
T*
(- Initial load: GET /workspace/messages.) Tj
T*
(- Send message: POST /workspace/messages with {user,text}.) Tj
T*
(- The POST returns updated message array, immediately reflected in UI.) Tj
T*
(- Messages authored by current user are visually separated using conditional class "own".) Tj
T*
T*
(2.8 Visualization dashboard) Tj
T*
(Visualization.jsx:) Tj
T*
(- Fetches workspace once and isolates tasks assigned to logged-in user.) Tj
T*
(- Computes total/completed/pending/completion rate.) Tj
T*
(- Uses Recharts for:) Tj
T*
( bar chart \(tasks by priority\)) Tj
T*
( pie chart \(completed vs remaining\)) Tj
T*
(- Also includes textual priority bars to keep summary visible without interpreting charts.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.9 Management console \(admin/manager operations\)) Tj
T*
(Management.jsx supports full team operations:) Tj
T*
(- Team member CRUD:) Tj
T*
( add member -> POST /workspace/members) Tj
T*
( remove member -> DELETE /workspace/members/:memberId) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
