(- Task lifecycle:) Tj
T*
( create assigned task with description/priority/due date) Tj
T*
( toggle task complete) Tj
T*
( edit title and due date) Tj
T*
( comment on task) Tj
T*
( delete task) Tj
T*
(- Activity feed:) Tj
T*
( GET /workspace/activity?limit=10&page=1) Tj
T*
(- Uses syncWorkspace helper to keep members/tasks coherent after mutations.) Tj
T*
(- Performs periodic refetch after writes to keep activity and board state consistent.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.10 Profile and account maintenance) Tj
T*
(ProfileSettings.jsx:) Tj
T*
(- GET /users/me for profile hydration.) Tj
T*
(- PATCH /users/me for name/phone/\(role when allowed server-side\).) Tj
T*
(- PATCH /users/me/password for credential rotation.) Tj
T*
(- Updates localStorage.loggedInUser after profile save.) Tj
T*
T*
(2.11 Navigation shell) Tj
T*
(Navbar.jsx and Footer.jsx provide app-level chrome.) Tj
T*
(- Navbar handles logout by clearing token + user and redirecting to /login.) Tj
T*
(- Contacts.jsx is static owner contact information.) Tj
T*
T*
(3\) Backend Architecture) Tj
T*
(3.1 Process startup and DB connectivity) Tj
T*
(server/server.js:) Tj
T*
(- Loads environment via dotenv.) Tj
T*
(- Resolves MONGO_URI \(or MONGO_URL fallback\) and MONGO_DB_NAME.) Tj
T*
(- Fails fast if URI missing.) Tj
T*
(- Connects to MongoDB with serverSelectionTimeoutMS=10000.) Tj
T*
(- Starts HTTP listener only after successful DB connection.) Tj
T*
T*
(3.2 Express app setup) Tj
T*
(server/app.js:) Tj
T*
(- Enables JSON body parsing.) Tj
T*
(- Applies manual CORS policy:) Tj
T*
( allows origins matching /^http://localhost:\\d+$/) Tj
T*
( allows methods GET,POST,PUT,PATCH,DELETE,OPTIONS) Tj
T*
( allows headers Content-Type, Authorization) Tj
T*
( handles preflight OPTIONS with 200) Tj
T*
(- Mounts route modules:) Tj
T*
( /api/users) Tj
T*
( /api/workspace) Tj
T*
(- Exposes health endpoint /api/health.) Tj
T*
T*
(3.3 Authentication and authorization middleware) Tj
T*
ET
