(middleware/auth.js:) Tj
T*
(- requireAuth:) Tj
T*
( parses Bearer token from Authorization header) Tj
T*
( verifies JWT using JWT_SECRET) Tj
T*
( attaches payload to req.user) Tj
T*
( returns 401 on missing/invalid/expired token) Tj
T*
(- requireRole\(...roles\):) Tj
T*
( enforces role-based access and returns 403 on mismatch) Tj
T*
T*
(3.4 User module) Tj
T*
(Routes \(routes/userRoutes.js\):) Tj
T*
(- GET /api/users \(management only\)) Tj
T*
(- POST /api/users and POST /api/users/signup \(create user\)) Tj
T*
(- DELETE /api/users/:id \(management only\)) Tj
T*
(- POST /api/users/login) Tj
T*
(- GET /api/users/me) Tj
T*
(- PATCH /api/users/me) Tj
T*
(- PATCH /api/users/me/password) Tj
T*
T*
(Controller highlights \(controllers/userController.js\):) Tj
T*
(- createUsers:) Tj
T*
( validates required fields and role enum) Tj
T*
( rejects duplicate email) Tj
T*
( hashes password with bcrypt salt rounds 10) Tj
T*
(- loginUser:) Tj
T*
( validates role selection and role-account consistency) Tj
T*
( supports legacy plaintext password migration to bcrypt on successful login) Tj
T*
( issues JWT \(7d\) containing id/email/role/name) Tj
T*
(- updateProfile:) Tj
T*
( allows name/phone updates for self) Tj
T*
( allows role update only when caller is management) Tj
T*
(- changePassword:) Tj
T*
( verifies current password then writes new bcrypt hash) Tj
T*
T*
(3.5 Workspace module) Tj
T*
(Routes \(routes/workspaceRoutes.js\):) Tj
T*
(- All workspace routes are auth-protected via router.use\(requireAuth\).) Tj
T*
(- Management-only operations:) Tj
T*
( add/remove members, delete task, fetch activity log.) Tj
T*
T*
(Controller highlights \(controllers/workspaceController.js\):) Tj
T*
(- getOrCreateWorkspace:) Tj
T*
( ensures a singleton workspace document exists.) Tj
T*
(- Legacy cleanup:) Tj
T*
( detects historical seeded placeholder members and removes them once.) Tj
T*
(- getTasks:) Tj
T*
