( supports server-side filtering by text, priority, status, assignedTo with pagination.) Tj
T*
(- addTask/updateTask/toggleTask/deleteTask:) Tj
T*
( task lifecycle mutations with validation and activity audit logging.) Tj
T*
(- addTaskComment:) Tj
T*
( appends comment entries directly under task.comments.) Tj
T*
(- getMessages/addMessage:) Tj
T*
( chat persistence in workspace.messages with paging for read path.) Tj
T*
(- getActivityLog:) Tj
