T*
T*
(4\) Data Model Design) Tj
T*
(4.1 User model) Tj
T*
(Collection: users) Tj
T*
(Fields:) Tj
T*
(- name \(required\)) Tj
T*
(- email \(required, unique, lowercase, trim\)) Tj
T*
(- password \(required, min 6, bcrypt hash\)) Tj
T*
(- phone \(optional string\)) Tj
T*
(- role \(management | team_member\)) Tj
T*
(- timestamps) Tj
T*
T*
(4.2 Workspace model \(single-document aggregate\)) Tj
T*
(Collection: workspaces) Tj
T*
(Top-level fields:) Tj
T*
(- teamName, teamHead, leaderContact) Tj
T*
(- members[]) Tj
T*
(- tasks[]) Tj
T*
(- messages[]) Tj
T*
(- activityLog[]) Tj
T*
T*
(Embedded schemas:) Tj
T*
(- member: {name}) Tj
T*
(- task: {title,description,priority,done,assignedTo,dueDate,comments[]}) Tj
T*
(- comment: {user,text,createdAt}) Tj
T*
(- message: {user,text,createdAt}) Tj
T*
(- activityLog: {actor,action,targetType,targetId,details,createdAt}) Tj
T*
T*
(Tradeoff note:) Tj
T*
(- Single workspace document simplifies transactions and retrieval for small-medium teams.) Tj
T*
(- As activity/messages/tasks scale, document size and update contention can become a bottleneck.) Tj
T*
T*
(5\) End-to-End Request Flows) Tj
T*
(5.1 Login flow) Tj
T*
(1. Frontend POST /api/users/login.) Tj
T*
ET
